&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Five (5) years of relevant experience with AV engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have an active DoD Top Secret clearance at a minimum&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have one (1) of the following certifications:
&lt;ul&gt;
